<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lyk yạ rb wḥdk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lyk yạ rb wḥdk .. kl ạlhtạf wạlḥmd
 (ạ̉sjd wạsbḥ ạsmk .. lạ̉nk qbltny)2
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉hdyk yạ rb sẖkry .. wqlby yrnm lyk
 ạ̉gẖny wạrfʿ ạsmk .. ʿlsẖạn qlbk kbyr
 ạ̉hdyk yạ rb ʿmry .. wkl ḥby lyk
 ạ̉gẖny wạrfʿ ạsmk .. ʿlsẖạn ḥbk gẖzyr
 2- lmạ knt fy bʿdy .. wạlsẖr fy qlby ktyr
 (rfʿt ʿny dẖnwby .. wạdtny qlb jdyd)2
 3- ḥty̱ fy wqt ḍʿfy .. wlmạ ạ̉kwn tʿbạn
 (ạ̹ydk bḥnạn tdạwyny .. wḥḍnk yḍmny)2</lyrics>
<author>mạjd jrjs, mạjd jrjs</author>
